window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>Outer Dark</i> is a novel at once fabular and starkly evocative, set is an unspecified place in Appalachia, sometime around the turn of the century.&nbsp;A woman bears her brother's child, a boy; he leaves the baby in the woods and tells her he died of natural causes.&nbsp;Discovering her brother's lie, she sets forth alone to find her son.&nbsp;Both brother and sister wander separately through a countryside being scourged by three terrifying and elusive strangers, headlong toward an eerie, apocalyptic resolution.</p>"; 
